Comment: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:37.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}無慈悲に告げる
Comment: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:44.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}君は  一人
Comment: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:50.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を  聞いてた
Comment: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:56.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}僕は  遠い
Comment: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:03.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}夢を  見てた
Comment: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を選び取る
Comment: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を諦める
Comment: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}決めようとしてる
Comment: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}僕は何様だ
Comment: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を選ぶかは
Comment: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}もう決まっている
Comment: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:14.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}間違いは無いか
Comment: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}神に問いかける
Comment: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}一人きりじゃなかった
Comment: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}ずっとそばにいたんだ
Comment: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:28.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}この手を伸ばす
Comment: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:32.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}怖いものなんかない
Comment: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}たとえ化け物になろうとも
Comment: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:43.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}成し遂げる
Comment: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:28.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}崩坏的终焉之世
Comment: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:37.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}无情告知
Comment: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:44.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}你默默一人
Comment: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:50.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}在聆听什么
Comment: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:56.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}而我恍惚
Comment: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:03.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}如在远梦中彷徨
Comment: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}选择什么
Comment: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}放弃什么
Comment: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}我有何权力
Comment: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}做这些决定
Comment: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}如何选择
Comment: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}已经确定
Comment: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:14.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}有否错误
Comment: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}向神询问
Comment: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}你不是一个人
Comment: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}一直在你身边
Comment: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:28.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}将这双手伸出
Comment: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:32.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}无所畏惧
Comment: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}就算是化身怪物
Comment: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:43.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}定将完成夙愿
